39341	AA32FF	Seal: Archosaur	^ffcb4aRead the notice if you are not clear in the area: \rThe enemy left a message in the dock. \rWatch and ask NPC. \rLight is untraceable. \rLook for the Holy Sword. \rPick up something before you leave. \rThere's something mysterious in the shallow water. \rThe eastern visitor can help you. \rThink about your current life.	1	16435	0
39342	AA32FF	Seal: Harshlands	^ffcb4aRead the notice if you are not clear in the area: \rThe NPC likes wandering. \rHidden in the ugly huge pile. \rVengeful Troops invade, people are afraid of them. \rThe origin is in the center of the land. \Don't care if the honey is sweet or not. \rReborn for love. \rThere are spells in the deep realms. \rGlacia is awful. \rEveryone will get its result and destiny.	1	16435	0
39343	AA32FF	Seal: Frozen River	^ffcb4aRead the notice if you are not clear in the area: \rShadows are in the cold water. \You can not see the enemies. \There are millions of enemies. \rRetreat first and get the clue. \Look for fire and burn the barrier. \To the depraved, just leave them alone. \rFight until the end. \rFight against the old opponents. \rThe seal is removed, and the Glacier opens.	1	16435	0
39344	AA32FF	Seal: Canyon	^ffcb4aRead the notice if you are not clear in the area: \rGoothe is made of ice and wears snow. \rThe steadiest structure is cut off gradually. \rUse the old ritual to summon. \rThe cold ice in the vent forms into air. \rThe enemies are hidden in the gully. \rThe armors are split, and the drumbeat strikes. \rThe day is not clear, and the enemies are not new. \The seal comes out when the Dog Moment arrives.	1	16435	0
39345	AA32FF	Seal: Tai Chi Shore	^ffcb4aRead the notice if you are not clear in the area: \rThe old track is clear. \rRelease the souls, thunder utters. \The coldest thing takes the thunder down. \rThe Darkness rushes with ice flakes. \rThe burning sword burns the ice. \rEmpyrean Slither, die! \rThe demon in the past, turns to tears now!	1	16435	0
39346	AA32FF	Seal: Volcanic Purgatory	^ffcb4aRead the notice if you are not clear in the area: \rThe Vengeful Troops kill, but get help. \rThe land should be protected, but get stuck. \rProtecting Pillar is in the sun. \rFearful, and void. \rIt burns and breaks its heart. \rIt declears war to the death on the peak.	1	16435	0
39347	AA32FF	Seal: Misfortune City	^ffcb4aRead the notice if you are not clear in the area: \rWatches highly for thousands of years. \rThere are pikes in the water. \rThe soul speaks its mind in the night. \rTreasure among the ruins. \rSacrifice for peace. \rThe old host tells you something by the way. \Kill it as all in the city wishes you do.	1	16435	0
39348	AA32FF	Seal: Snake Isle	^ffcb4aRead the notice if you are not clear in the area: \rThe 3 islands are in blue. \rThe wine is delicious, but people can't be drunk. \The Sky of Three Creatures doesn't reach the sky. \rWeird heads are on the ground, coins are everywhere, and blood is dried up. \rThe Earth of Three Creatures absorbed land before. \rThe Human of Three Creatures is good looking, but malicious. \rThe water origin turns out to be a dragon. \rIt breaks the sky and removes the barrier.	1	16435	0
39349	AA32FF	Mystery Book¬∑Hiil of the Swarm	^ffcb4aRead this notice if you are new to the area:\rThe Warriors are busy in front of the Walled Stronghold.\rIt's their duty to protect this ancient place.\rWhere did the strange rocks come from?\rGreen Wood indicates the trace.\rThe blue light is quite odd.\rTime and space warps here, opening a channel to the mortal world\rMonsters must be stopped.\rSeek help from the Elder.\rShift the fire to attract attention.\rThe crisis at Hill of the Swarm can be eased.\rAnd the seal can be broken.	1	16435	0
39350	AA32FF	N/AÁß∞Âè∑ÊèêÁ§∫ÈÅìÂÖ∑010	^ffcb4aThe Elder of Etherblade writes\rabout the Sword Aura that protects\r the city:\rThe true strength of a city comes\rfrom its commerce: the Pawnshops and\rBankers, its travelling Merchants, its\rSeamstresses and Tailors. Forge these\rtogether like a Blacksmith, and any\rdark Seal placed upon your city will\rbe washed away with the waters of the\rsacred waterfall.	1	16435	0
