39361	AA32FF	N/AÁß∞Âè∑ÊèêÁ§∫ÈÅìÂÖ∑021	^ffcb4aRead this notice if you are unclear about the area.\rThe dragon has brought peace to Archosaur,\rand the fox has been flushed out from his Lightsail Cave.\rThieves lurk in the west,\rthe Psychic knows best,\rand three Sages watch over all.\rA hidden threat to Archosaur grows,\rand the seal must be broken to save it.	1	16435	0
39362	AA32FF	N/AÁß∞Âè∑ÊèêÁ§∫ÈÅìÂÖ∑022	^ffcb4aIf it's treasure and adventure you seek, then read on:\rThe old woman beside the river is both merciful, and mysterious.\rThe heartbroken have no need for momentos.\rThe stubborn prince has a hole in his pockets.\rThe Winged Tiger has lost his treasure.\rThe Turtlemaster never did.\rA once fallen friend has risen again as an enemy.\rDreams come true when all wish for the same.\rStealthily the river flows.\rThe dragons may prove unreliable.	1	16435	0
