39364	AA32FF	N/AÁß∞Âè∑ÊèêÁ§∫ÈÅìÂÖ∑024	^ffcb4aThe beautiful Nessina has a sorrowful tale of woe.\rLike many men before him, hers left to face their foe.\rHis cause was great and noble, his selfless soul divine,\ryet after all he sacrificed, his name is lost to time.\rFor when the field grows quiet, and the smoke of battle clears,\rno rousing tale of victory can dry a widow's tears.	1	16435	0
39365	AA32FF	N/AÁß∞Âè∑ÊèêÁ§∫ÈÅìÂÖ∑025	^ffcb4aIf it is a grand venture you seek, please read this script in detail: \rOnce upon a time, a legend was born in the Town of Arrivals. \rHe was brave and fearless, trying to take down an infamous Bulldoc. \rBut the tale was lost, along with the Dorim Codex.\rNow, with the Dorim Codex reclaimed, a mysterious ancient ruin has been revealed.\rBeneath the ruins are the continuation of the very tale we are seeking.\rForeign siblings were at peace, but not for long.\rNow the dragon wilderness is about to be set aflame, and they will not turn a blind eye.\rIf you are truly the chosen one, seek the Dragon Vein underneath the grand chasm of Dragon Wilderness.	1	16435	0
