39367	AA32FF	N/AÁß∞Âè∑ÊèêÁ§∫ÈÅìÂÖ∑027	^ffcb4aIf it is a grand venture you seek, please read this script in detail: \rA seal locking away souls.\rEnemies nearby set to interrupt.\rA tall goblet full of mystical liquid.\rA powerful artifact to power the rest.\rFinal words of advice from the caravan.\rA stolen treasure to soothe the spirits.\rAnd at the gate of a portal, the preparations are complete.	1	16435	0
