41084	FF0000	White Emperor: Alexander	^ffcb4aThe Light Emperor, first king of the Light Nation. In his\ryouth, he led his army in battle against 400,000 soldiers from\rthe north. After claiming victory, he was elected king by 36\rwarlords, and established the capital city of Everfall.	1	16407	2147483711
41085	FF0000	Eldros	^ffcb4aThe Frost Emperor, a great king who unified the north and\rexpanded his rule southward. Aftering suffering defeat at the\rhands of Alexander, he retreated back to the north frontier\rand built Glacier City, capital of the Frost Nation.	1	16407	2147483711
41772	FF0000	Ying Siga	^ffcb4aThe headstrong Emperor of the Flame Nation, and patriarch\rof the Fire Dragon Clan. With unshakable pride and ambition,\rhe established Durna, capital of the Flame Nation.	1	16407	2147483711
41773	FF0000	Mayen	^ffcb4aThe daughter of Janice, the first Dark Empress. She inherited\rthe throne at the tender age of 18 and built the City of Peace,\rwhere she ruled as the Dark Empress.	1	16407	2147483711
41774	FF0000	Dorian	^ffcb4aThe Dark Emperor, a man of the sea and master naval strategist,\rleads the Twilight Empire and rules the waters. Though he is an\remperor, his appearance and mannerisms are like those of a sea\rbrigand.	1	16407	2147483711
41775	FF0000	Lord Tyrant	^ffcb4aThe emperor of the Primal World. After the gods abandoned the\rPrimal World, he ensured the survival of his people and built a\rnew empire.He eventually became a greedy Tyrant hated by all.	1	16407	2147483711
41784	FF6000	Althea	^ffcb4aThe noble queen of the Light Nation. A strong but benevolent\rruler, she is greatly adored by all her people and soldiers.	1	16407	2147483711
41785	FF6000	Kestra	^ffcb4aThe empress of the Frost Nation, she eternally craves absolute\rpower. When she blows her horn, hundreds of thousands of\rbarbarians will respond with a roar.	1	16407	2147483711
41786	FF6000	Astrid	^ffcb4aDescending from fire dragons, Empress Astrid is a master of flames.\rHer dragon blood allows her to connect with and tame the fiercest\rof dragons, but has also endowed her with a hot head and short\rtemper.	1	16407	2147483711
41787	FF6000	Lorelei	^ffcb4aThough gentle in appearance, Lorelei, queen of the Twilight\rEmpire, is a true veteran of the seas. She is the captain of\rthe Dragonlord, an impressive warship. Sharp and aloof, she can\rcome across as intimidating even to her own soldiers.	1	16407	2147483711
41788	FF6000	Gu Hensin	^ffcb4aThe pike is the most difficult blade to wield with control. And\ryet, despite his young age, Gu Hensin wields it as if it were a\rpart of his body.	1	16407	2147483711
41789	FF6000	Lio Gianni	^ffcb4aLio Gianni is one of the Four Great Commanders. In the Battle\rof Two Cities, the Winged Elves dispatched all of their elite\rtroops, but Lio Gianni's brilliant strategies pushed them back\rwhile optimizing the city's defenses.	1	16407	2147483711
41790	FF6000	Tsen the Heavensent	^ffcb4aTsen the Heavensent, one of the Four Great Commanders, does not\rhave any family. Contrary to his nickname, he is a cruel man on\rthe battlefield, showing no mercy to his enemies.	1	16407	2147483711
41791	FF6000	Fen the Victorious	^ffcb4aThe charismatic leader of Four Great Commanders. He has\r claimed countless victories in battle, even when outnumbered. \rThis valiant man was feared by the Winged Elves. Unfortunately,\rthe gods took him away, for his godlike strength threw the world\rinto imbalance.	1	16407	2147483711
41792	FF6000	Ancestor Feng Loriel	^ffcb4aFeng Lorie, the Tideborn's ancestor, was a brave and resourceful\rman. He killed Turoho, the evil god of the Nightspikes, with Lunar\rDissector, putting an end to the war between the Tideborn and the\rNightspikes, which had lasted for a thousand years.	1	16407	2147483711
41793	FF6000	Saint Feng Drime	^ffcb4aIt is extremely difficult to reverse the Dimensional Cataclysm.\rAs the priestess of this ritual, Feng Drime overdrew her entire\rsoulforce to stop the curse from getting out of control, sacri-\rficing her life and soul for the sake of the Tideborn.	1	16407	2147483711
41794	FF6000	King Feng Triton	^ffcb4aThe king of the Tideborn who fought valiantly on the battle-\rfield for the survival of his people. Now, Feng Triton sits in\rhis palace above Raging Tide, picking up the wand or blowing\rthe horn now and then. Perhaps he is reminiscing on his days\rat war.	1	16407	2147483711
41795	FF6000	General Jen	^ffcb4aThe incumbent general who defends Plume City. Jen is an outsta-\rnding Winged Elf archer. It is said that anyone hit by Jen's\rice arrow will turn into a wisp of smoke.	1	16407	2147483711
41796	FF6000	General Chung	^ffcb4aThe incumbent general who defends Etherblade City. Chung's\rfather and grandfather also held this post before him. Chung\rdeeply loved Loyan, the daughter of the City Lord. After Loyan\rdied, the heartbroken Chung chose to remain single.	1	16407	2147483711
41797	FF6000	General Po	^ffcb4aThe incumbent general who defends the City of the Lost. \rGeneral Po is a master of forging weapons and armor. He once\rforged a set of extraordinary armor with the materials that he\rfound in the Twilight Temple. This armor made him nearly\rinvincible.	1	16407	2147483711
41798	FF6000	Elder of the Streams	^ffcb4aWhen the City of a Thousand Streams was built, all races and\rfactions sent their elites to stay in the Worldspire, making the\rcity a decisive force and global mediator in Perfect World. The\rElder of the Streams is the spokesman of the city and makes all\rthe important decisions that could affect all of Perfect World.	1	16407	2147483711
41799	FF6000	Elder of Archosaur	^ffcb4aAs the most famous of the five major capitals, Archosaur is the\rcenter of political and cultural exchanges in Perfect World. All\rElders of Archosaur have, in the past, wholly devoted themselves\rto serving this city.	1	16407	2147483711
41800	FF6000	Radiance	^ffcb4aSelected by the gods, Radiance was the founder of Earthguard.\rTo defeat Dark Radiance, his evil counterpart, Radiance sacri-\rficed his own body. Since then, Radiance's nuema went missing.\rIt is said that the Illusive Faerie of the Forsaken Temple once\rcaught a glimpse of Radiance's wandering nuema.	1	16407	2147483711
41801	FF6000	Dark Radiance	^ffcb4aRadiance's dark half, formed from his evil thoughts. Seeking\rabsolute power, Dark Radiance devoured wraiths to strengthen\rhimself. After Radiance destroyed himself, Dark Radiance was\rsaved by the Wraith Lord, in turn becoming his executioner and\rslaughtering his victims.	1	16407	2147483711
41802	FF6000	Yi the Mighty Wing	^ffcb4aThe king of the Mighty Wings, one of four ancient Winged Elf\rnations. Allying with the other Winged Elf nations, he once\rcrusaded against the Twilight Empire. Protected by the Might of\rthe Great Goose, he survived the Twilight Disaster.	1	16407	2147483711
41803	FF6000	Feather Lord	^ffcb4aAn ancient Winged Elf king. Allying with Ien the Arbor, he\rhelped defeat the Twilight Empire's army.	1	16407	2147483711
41804	FF6000	Ien the Arbor	^ffcb4aAn ancient Winged Elf king. Allying with the Feather Lord, he\rhelped defeat the Twilight Empire's army.	1	16407	2147483711
41805	FF6000	Yi the Earthquake	^ffcb4aAn ancient Winged Elf king famous for defeating General Chongo\rin the battle against the Twilight Empire.	1	16407	2147483711
41806	FF6000	Tsu	^ffcb4aThe second minister of the Twilight Empire, as well as the\rleader of a faction supporting Prince Chongming. She orchest-\rrated the undercover uprising within the Twilight Empire along\rwith Tsuan. She also started the Wheel of Fate in the battle\ragainst the Winged Elf Alliance that resulted in the destruction\rof the Twilight Empire.	1	16407	2147483711
41807	FF6000	Tsuan	^ffcb4aAn outstanding Winged Elf warrior. To overthrow the Twilight\rEmpire, Tsuan removed her plumes through the Sacrilege Ceremony\rand became the minister of Twilight Empire along with Tsu. They\rcleverly orchestrated an internal takeover of the Twilight\rEmpire's forces.	1	16407	2147483711
41808	FF6000	Yeh Kuhan	^ffcb4aA brave warrior with a penchant for flamboyant poetry.	1	16407	2147483711
41809	FF6000	Holeen	^ffcb4aFrost Ancient's brother, who was deserted at a burial site for\rdead infants. He survived by eating corpses and bones, and made\ra contract with Fientazzar, the enemy of Frostcovered City's\rguardian. He swore to rebuild Frostcovered City for himself and\rrespect Fientazzar as his god. He is known for his sadistic\rfighting style.	1	16407	2147483711
41810	FF6000	Vanished Ancestor	^ffcb4aVanished Ancestor, the grand wraith wizard, is sealed away in\rthe Temple of the Forbidden Coast by the Tideborn.	1	16407	2147483711
41811	FF6000	Harpy Wraith	^ffcb4aThe Harpy Wraith is a master of the dreaded Soul Trap. It has\rthe power to control the souls around it, and once the soul is\rcontrolled, it is forever slave to the Harpy Wraith.	1	16407	2147483711
41812	FF6000	Archdemon Isrifar	^ffcb4aLord Isrifar's awakened form. It is said that his obsession with\rpower drove him to become a demon.	1	16407	2147483711
41813	FF6000	General Summer	^ffcb4aThe commander of Archosaur, and a descendant of Lio Gianni. He\rleads the Allied Force against the Wraith Army, and is known as\rthe 'Iron Fortress of Archosaur.'	1	16407	2147483711
41814	FF6000	Emperor Tsang	^ffcb4aTsang, once a lord of Everfall, has become a hideous undead\rwalker of the illusory world	1	16407	2147483711
41815	FF6000	Princess of Moonlight	^ffcb4aDorian's daughter, known as the Beauty of the East. Since the\rcivil war, she has been imprisoned in the Desert Tower. No one\rhas known of her whereabouts since General Chongyun went to\rrescue her.	1	16407	2147483711
41816	FF6000	Chungyun	^ffcb4aGeneral Chongyun was a pioneer of the Twilight Army, succeeding\rin defending the Twilight Empire from the Winged Elves' siege.\rAfter the Plain War, he was appointed to bring the Princess of\rMoonlight back from the Desert Tower. However, he disappeared\rtogether with the Princess of Moonlight after defeating the\rNimbusians.	1	16407	2147483711
41817	FF6000	Lethal Vengeance	^ffcb4aLegendary devils who exist solely to destroy. When the Twilight\rEmpire was going through a great crisis, Minister Tsu activated\rthe Wheel of Fate to release the sealed ancient devils. The\rceremonylasted for 49 days, consuming rich sacrificial offer-\rings. However, an accidenthappened, and the devils destoryed\rthe Twilight Empire.	1	16407	2147483711
41818	FF6000	Armageddon	^ffcb4aThe creator of the Illusory World. After breaking away from the\rgods, she created an illusory world in which dead, powerful\rcreatures are revived. She summons ancient mystical powers to\rstrengthen the illusory world, hoping to replace the world created\rby the gods with her undead world.	1	16407	2147483711
41819	FF6000	Elven Priest Yuusa	^ffcb4aThe highest priest of Winged Elf who believes that the gods will\rreturn someday. Managing the internal affairs in Plume City along-\rside the Elders, she is considered the spiritual leader of the\rWinged Elves.	1	16407	2147483711
41820	FF6000	Plume City Elder	^ffcb4aAn Elder of five races, in charge of Winged Elf affairs.	1	16407	2147483711
41821	FF6000	Etherblade Elder	^ffcb4aAn Elder of five races, in charge of Human affairs.	1	16407	2147483711
41822	FF6000	Elder Star	^ffcb4aAn Elder of five races, in charge of Earthguard affairs.	1	16407	2147483711
41823	FF6000	Elder Yashimo	^ffcb4aAn Elder of Earthguard, enjoying the highest prestige in the \rSacred Word. He can hear the whispers from gods, converting\rthose poor souls into Earthguards..	1	16407	2147483711
41824	FF6000	Yelling to the Sky	^ffcb4aThe wraiths in the Deserted Sea near the Hidden Dragon Den\rspent many years creating a powerful devil. Hiding deep in the\rHidden Dragon Den, the ferocious devil waits for people who are\rled there by the Fire Dragon Clan.	1	16407	2147483711
41825	FF6000	City of the Lost Elder	^ffcb4aAn Elder of five races, in charge of Untamed affairs.	1	16407	2147483711
41826	FF6000	Beastmaster Hokka	^ffcb4aWild and strong from birth, he was give nthe title 'King of Beasts'\rby the Untamed Elders for his great war feats. In his later years,\rhe pioneered many skills that are now essential, such as Stomp of\rthe Beast King, Beast King's Inspiration, Bestial Onslaught, and\rBestial Rage.	1	16407	2147483711
41827	FF6000	Emperor Aurogon	^ffcb4aAbsorbing the consciousness of all beings in this world, the\rWheel of Eternity grew a self-awareness that attracts wraiths.\rAurogon, the serpent demon, was born as a result of this.	1	16407	2147483711
41828	FF6000	Tiger Won	^ffcb4aThis brilliant inventor designed the Human's crystal-powered\rAerosword, and helped the Untamed domesticate the first Sparrow\rHawks.	1	16407	2147483711
41829	FF6000	Anonymous Wiseman	^ffcb4aIn the middle of the first Millennium War, a gravely ill man\rfrom the Primal World helped the Humans with his marvelous\rpyrocraft. He made some improvements to the pyrogram spell,\rgreatly enhancing its firing range. These developments turned\rthe tide of battle.	1	16407	2147483711
41830	FF6000	Jane the Harper	^ffcb4aThe first queen of the Ancestral Land, and the mother of Mayen,\rthe Green Empress. She fell in Pon Jay, a wizard from Etherblade\rCity who later died in a battle against the Fire Dragon Clan.\rWhen Mayen was old enough to inherit the throne, Janice\rpeacefully joined her husband in death.	1	16407	2147483711
41831	FF6000	Grand Wizard Tensa	^ffcb4aGrand Wizard Tensa is the most powerful Human wizardof all time.\rShe is the one who created the Undine Strike and Soporific Whisper\rtechniques.	1	16407	2147483711
41832	FF6000	Soul Controller Saki	^ffcb4aAs a disciple of Tensa, Soul Controller Saki became the first\rpsychic. Due to her ability to control soulforce instead of\relements, Saki was not regarded by traditional wizards. Instead,\rshe taught her skills to the Tideborn, who were eager to achieve\rpsychic powers.	1	16407	2147483711
41833	FF6000	The Incacerate	^ffcb4aThe supreme commander of the Wraith Army, and a man of great\rwisdom and power, he takes charge of this mysterious army under\rthe orders of the Wraith Ancestor. Fearless and uncompromising,\rhe marches forward in battle with frightening willpower.	1	16407	2147483711
41834	FF6000	Winged Commander	^ffcb4aA powerful man who controls the Archosaur Commanders. He is as\rambitious as he is calculating, always watching and waiting in\rsilence for the perfect strike.	1	16407	2147483711
41835	FF6000	General Helian	^ffcb4aAn outstanding general who is greatly respected by his subordinates.	1	16407	2147483711
41836	FFD700	Heavenly Tiger	^ffcb4aAn elusive ancient beast from Lothranis.	1	16407	2147483711
41837	FFD700	Demonic Tiger	^ffcb4aAn elusive ancient beast from Momaganon.	1	16407	2147483711
41838	FFD700	Thom Mundan	^ffcb4aOne of Three Demons from Abaddon who has slaughtered countless\rinnocent people.	1	16407	2147483711
41839	FFD700	Gaurnob Guard	^ffcb4aOne of Three Demons in Abaddon who possesses boundless strength.	1	16407	2147483711
41840	FFD700	Monoblat Dracoboa	^ffcb4aOne of Three Demons in Abaddon who tortures\rits victims with fire magic.	1	16407	2147483711
41841	FFD700	Infernal Spikewing	^ffcb4aInfernal Spikewing, one of the Three Fallen Celestials, was\ronce a defender of Lothranis. Tempted by the evil power in the\rSeat of Torment, his body deformed into that of a hideous demon.	1	16407	2147483711
41842	FFD700	Rancid Venerator	^ffcb4aRancid Venerator, one of the Three Fallen Celestials, was once\ra defender of Lothranis. Tempted by the evil power in the Seat\rof Torment, his body deformed into that of a hideous demon.	1	16407	2147483711
41843	FFD700	Torturess Venerator	^ffcb4aTorturess Venerator, one of the Three Fallen Celestials, was once\ra defender of Lothranis. Tempted by the evil power in the Seat\rof Torment, his body deformed into that of a hideous demon.	1	16407	2147483711
41844	FFD700	Dread Lord Hengchih	^ffcb4aSince the City of Abominations was built, the creatures living\rthere have been protecting a secret magic buried underground.\rRumor has it that it was a forbidden magic of destructive power.\rWhen the nine stars formed a straight line Dread Lord Hengchih\rtook the opportunity to occupy the City of Abominations, in\rorder to get the secret magic.	1	16407	2147483711
41845	FFD700	Chaotic Ravager	^ffcb4aBorn in discord and buried in silence, Chaos is the omnipotent\roverlord of everything. He has the power to influence fate itself.	1	16407	2147483711
41846	FFD700	Wolfen Ironside	^ffcb4aA war hero of the Primal World, Wolfen Ironside is powerful\rand mighty. However, he is cruel and boorish to people.	1	16407	2147483711
41847	FFD700	Lady Frostburn	^ffcb4aA demon formed completely from essences, unbound by the laws\rof physics. She is as old as the universe itself. It is impossible\r to kill such a demon.	1	16407	2147483711
41848	FFD700	Ultimate Stance	^ffcb4aUltimate Stance is an intelligent beast proficient in\rwarcraft. All beasts revere him.	1	16407	2147483711
41849	FFD700	Primeval Elemental	^ffcb4aIn ancient books, this god is often described as a being that\rgoverns the elemental powers and is one with the universe.	1	16407	2147483711
41850	FFD700	Shonabu	^ffcb4aHe used to be an immortal poet. Because of his immortality, he\rlacked appreciation for life and death, and was corrupted by\revil. He coins beautiful lyrics as he murders his victims.	1	16407	2147483711
41851	FFD700	Astaria	^ffcb4aA beautiful butterfly spirit inhabiting the valleys. Its long\rcultivationhas blessed it with great power - power that it will\rnot hesitate to use against strangers.	1	16407	2147483711
41852	FFD700	Madam Sadi	^ffcb4aOne of the Raksa Lords, who presides over the Demonic Prison.\rHer biggest obsession is inventing new torture devices and list-\rening to the prisoners' screams.	1	16407	2147483711
41853	FFD700	Dismal Duke	^ffcb4aThe Dismal Duke is one of the few intellectual Wraiths, and is\ra cruel extremist. His radical nature and insane boldness have\rwon him a high reputation among the Wraiths. His Wraith divisions\rfamous for their speed, often showing appearing out of nowhere\rin unexpected places. Once they almost marched into Archosaur\rCity. Many Wraiths believe he is the greatest among their ranks,\rand their true leader.	1	16407	2147483711
41854	FFD700	Dimentora	^ffcb4aA suit of armor worn by its dead owner in an ancient tomb. The\rdark, arcane power of the tomb gave the armor sentience. Rest-\rless, it began to protect its master's corpsepunishing all who\rdare venture into the tomb.	1	16407	2147483711
41855	FFD700	Burial Inferno	^ffcb4aA champion of the Hidden Dragon Den monsters who craves the\rpower of fire, believing it is the only true strength. This\robsessive belief, however, led it to the dark side.	1	16407	2147483711
41856	FFD700	Chin Wuming	^ffcb4aOnce a close friend to Fei Kungxing and Yeh Kuhan, he abandoned\rhis friends due to their differences and pursued the demonic\rway. However, he still possesses a pitiful heart.	1	16407	2147483711
41857	FFD700	Fei Kungxing	^ffcb4aOnce a close friend to Chin Wuming and Yeh Kuhan, he abandoned\rhis friends due to their differences. He was nearly killed by the\rThundersoul Beast when during his weakest moment. The beast\rcontinues to haunt him in his nightmares.	1	16407	2147483711
41858	FFD700	Miss Chiu	^ffcb4a'Only the fallen leaf knows that it is autumn.\rEvery night it sleeps in frosty tears.'	1	16407	2147483711
41859	FFD700	King Kisian	^ffcb4aAn immortal king who led the ancient people of Perfect World\rand Morai in the war that defeated Aurogon and brought many\ryears of peace.	1	16407	2147483711
41860	FFD700	Prophet Mogo	^ffcb4aThe mysterious leader of the Shroud. His unique magical powers\rallow him to walk freely among the living and the dead.	1	16407	2147483711
41861	FFD700	Lord Gugg	^ffcb4aThe man who leads a large army made of elites from Corona and\rShroud. He built the army in support of the\balance of powers,\rmaking him one of three great powers. However, no one knows his\rtrue identity.	1	16407	2147483711
41862	FFD700	Emissary of Light	^ffcb4aA low-ranking envoy of the Divine Furies, whose duty is\rto present newbies with quests.	1	16407	2147483711
