41866	FFD700	Emissary of Shroud	^ffcb4aAn envoy sent to Shroud by the Divine Furies. It seems that every\rmajor warof the past was related to the Divine Furies.	1	16407	2147483711
41867	FFD700	Emissary of Luminance	^ffcb4aAn envoy sent to Luminance by the Divine Furies. It seems that every major war\rof the past was related to the Divine Furies.	1	16407	2147483711
41868	FFD700	Puppeteer	^ffcb4aThe Puppeteer is the most loyal servant of Lord Borobodur. He\rguards the gate to his lord's chamber and shows no mercy to\rthose who set foot into the place. He often imprisons his victims\rin a tiny room until they break down in madness.	1	16407	2147483711
41869	FFD700	Mask of Grief	^ffcb4aThe Mask of Grief was born from the good side of Lord Borobudur.\rHowever, it is still bound to the evil lord, forced to do its\rbidding. It bravely asked to be killed by a warrior of justice,\rso as to weaken its evil half.	1	16407	2147483711
41870	FFD700	Leaf Rain Dryad	^ffcb4aPeachblossom Ritualist's sister, who also lived in Lothranis.\rAfter Peachblossom Fairy bacame Peachblossom Ritualist, she\rfollowed her to Momaganon and abandoned her celestial form.	1	16407	2147483711
41871	FFD700	Borobudur Lord	^ffcb4aLord Borobudur possesses god-like power. He was contained by a\rgroup of seven celestial warriors after a five day fight and\rsealed in Abaddon. When Peachblossom Ritualist was injured,\rhe broke the seal and began his conquest of Momaganon.	1	16407	2147483711
41872	FFD700	Peachblossom Ritualist	^ffcb4a'Do you truly wish to give up life as a celestial being and\rbecome a demon?' asked the Celestial Demon. The Fairy answered,\r'I am no longer the person I was. There's no place in the Celestial\rRealm for me anymore. Please take me away.'	1	16407	2147483711
41873	FFD700	Queen Xipher	^ffcb4aThe Queen of Demons. As a powerful, respected, and ambitious\rwarrior, she may be intending to usurp the Hellfire Abomination's\rrule.	1	16407	2147483711
41874	FFD700	Trap Master Fierce	^ffcb4aThe demon lord who followed Queen Xipher after the Seat of\rTorment changed. He is an expert machinist who guards the Hell\rTrap for Queen Xipher, while preparing new forces for the reborn\rdarkness.	1	16407	2147483711
41875	FFD700	Lord of Captivation	^ffcb4aThe bastard son of the Hellfire Abomination. He inherited his\rfather's short temper. After the Hellfire Abomination was locked\rinside the Seat of Torment, he became more aggessive and was\rfinally imprisoned in Seat of Torment as well. 	1	16407	2147483711
41876	FFD700	Hellfire Abomination	^ffcb4aHe once lived in Lothranis but was exiled to the Seat of\rTorment due to his cruel ways. The agony in the Seat of\rTorment intensifies his hatred for the world.	1	16407	2147483711
41877	FFD700	Guard Seven	^ffcb4aGuard Seven, defender of the west gate of Archosaur, bears no\rsympathy for the evil. He kills all wraiths and outlaws who come\rnear the gate.	1	16407	2147483711
41878	FFD700	Emperor Aohe	^ffcb4aThe cunning East Sovereign of Morai. He is a trickster who can\rtransform into different people. Shrewd and silent, he hides his\rown ambition when giving advice to Aurogon. He organizes a faction\rwith Yakku and Biran, conspiring on the sly.	1	16407	2147483711
41879	FFD700	Gorath	^ffcb4aThe miserly North Sovereign of Morai. Biran is despised by\rAurogon because he is a greedy coward. Aohe drew Biran to his\rside, valuing his powerful strength. Biran will betray anyone\ras long as it's profitable to do so.	1	16407	2147483711
41880	FFD700	Emperor Chigo	^ffcb4aThe headstrong Central Sovereign of Morai. Deeply trusted by\rAurogon, Chigo draws up the final plan. He kills Glory, the Elder's\rson, and takes on his appearance. Then, he activates the Undying\rDial, attempting to rebuild the wraith land.	1	16407	2147483711
41881	FFD700	Mistress of Night	^ffcb4aThe beautiful but capricious West Sovereign of Morai. Sometimes,\rshe is sweet and mild. Sometimes, she is quite cold-blooded. She\rhates men very much, but she obeys Aohe's every word.	1	16407	2147483711
41882	FFD700	Ghost Wing	^ffcb4aThe proud Upper Sovereign of Morai. As the overlord in the sky,\rhe possesses the sharpest eyes amongst the Sovereigns. Looking\rdown upon the other five sovereigns, he is only loyal and devoted\rto Aurogon, and ruthless to all creatures who enter his airspace.	1	16407	2147483711
41883	FFD700	Emperor Locen	^ffcb4aThe bloodthirsty South Sovereign of Morai. To him, there is no\rbetter pleasure than killing and pillaging. Leaving fire and\rdestruction in his wake, Locen truly is a monster.	1	16407	2147483711
41884	FFD700	Duke Blacke	^ffcb4aDuke Blacke is a knowledgeable man who lives in Archosaur. It\ris said that he has seven beautiful wives.	1	16407	2147483711
41885	FFD700	Celestial Sister	^ffcb4aThere is a gorgeous fairy living in the Frozen Hall of Frost-\rcovered City. You can only win her favor with Sincerity.	1	16407	2147483711
41886	FFD700	Tideborn Princess	^ffcb4aShe was once the princess of Tideborn. Tricked by \rVanished Ancestor, she fell into Palace of Nirvana \rand became Ashura Netherqueen.	1	16407	2147483711
41887	FFD700	Tideborn Princess	^ffcb4aA mystical woman with breathtaking beauty. It is saidrthat she\has the most alluring voice and dancing postures. But,no one\rknows where she came from or how she ended up in Perfect World.\rNumerous people around the world seek her, hoping to lay their\reyes upon her beauty.	1	16407	2147483711
41888	FFD700	Pestilent Destroyer	^ffcb4aA mystical and unfathomable warrior of the Wraith Army. It is\rsaid that he was transformed by the resentful souls of dead\rwraiths. This intense hatred grants him mysterious power. He\rhas sworn to kill everyone who challenges the Wraith Army.	1	16407	2147483711
41889	FFD700	Obscure Reaper	^ffcb4aThe powerful grand wizard of the Wraith Army. Residing in the\rdark demonic lake, he is odd and morose. Almost everyone who\rattempts to approach him is killed by his immense power.	1	16407	2147483711
41890	FFD700	Snakefist Guardian	^ffcb4aThe lonely and bloodthirsty swordsman of the Wraith Army. He\rwanders the underworld all day long, killing every living thing\rin his path.	1	16407	2147483711
41891	FFD700	Cannonfist Orclord	^ffcb4aA ruthless fighter of the Wraith Army. Nobody\rknows where he came from. With his flaming\rhammer, this strapping man kills everyone\rwho challenges the Wraith Army.	1	16407	2147483711
41892	FFD700	Shadowskull Lich	^ffcb4aAn evil sorcerer of the Wraith Army. His noble blood endows him\rwith fearsome magic powers, which have earned him the respect of\rthe Wraiths.	1	16407	2147483711
41893	FFD700	Warrior Trainer	^ffcb4aHumans are sociable, and the majority of them choose lives as\rmerchants and diplomats. Yet the few who take up arms are by no\rmeans less able. Gifted with an amazing flexibility, Humans\radapt easily to every new situation.	1	16407	2147483711
41894	FFD700	Mage Trainer	^ffcb4aWizards prefer to cast damaging spells from a distance. Though\rthey are masters of damaging Water, Fire, and Earth, their bodies\rare weak and not good at close combat.	1	16407	2147483711
41895	FFD700	Bestial Trainer	^ffcb4aThe Untamed are descendants of the animals \rthat evolved sentience. With berserker rage \rand animal cunning, they still carry the \rbeast in their hearts.	1	16407	2147483711
41896	FFD700	Fox Lady Trainer	^ffcb4aTrue to their heritage as self-aware foxes, serpents, and other\rvermin, the Venomancers are subtle, relying on poisons or curses\rto bring down enemies. They can also control animals or transform\rinto foxes for an additional set of skills.	1	16407	2147483711
41897	FFD700	Archer Trainer	^ffcb4aArchers hail from an ancient and divine bloodline. \rTheir exquisite form and unique wings grant them \rthe ability to fly. As the guardian of Winged Elf, they \rare outstanding archers and brave warriors, good at \rusing ranged weapons like the bow.	1	16407	2147483711
41898	FFD700	Priest Trainer	^ffcb4aThe Winged Elves are the most beautiful people among their\rcontemporaries. Gifted with flight from a young age, they can\rbe seemingly aloof and reclusive. Yet, those who are familiar\rwith them, find Winged Elves to be staunch allies.	1	16407	2147483711
41899	FFD700	Assassin Trainer	^ffcb4aStriking from the shadows, a dagger in the back, and a silent\rretreat are trademarks of an Assassin. Assassins are not brute\rmelee fighters, but masters of finesse. They prefer to rely on\ragility rather than bulky armor.	1	16407	2147483711
41900	FFD700	Psychic Trainer	^ffcb4aThe Tideborn class no longer pursue mastery of the elements,\rbut now manipulate the essence and instincts of creatures.\rThey manifest their will through Soulforce to enhance them-\rselves and their allies while harming their enemies.	1	16407	2147483711
41901	FFD700	Seeker Trainer	^ffcb4aSeekers train in both the martial and arcane arts, and use the\relement of metal to enhance their close-combat swordplay. Each\rSeeker bears a relic upon their forehead that can discern evil. 	1	16407	2147483711
41902	FFD700	Mystic Trainer	^ffcb4aA Mystic affects others with their grace and tenderness. With\rthe ability to communicate with the spiritual beings of nature,\rthey summon them as weapons. Vines, thorns, and trees are just a\rfraction of their arsenal. A Mystic also possesses miraculous\rhealing power, providing full support to teammates during combat. 	1	16407	2147483711
41903	FFD700	Overseer Aeban	^ffcb4aA valiant warlord whose origins are a mystery. He sometimes\rcomes to Perfect World to recruit the strongest of warriors\rinto the war between the four nations. He does not seem to\rhave a dedicated alliance with any of the nations.	1	16407	2147483711
