41970	AA32FF	Niang Hu	^ffcb4aA legendary venomancer, the ex-owner of the Khatru Pup.\rShe was victimized by a scheme and was accused of betraying her people.\rFortunately she realized her fault at last, \rand now she is imprisoned to remedy her guilt.	1	16407	2147483711
41971	AA32FF	Your name	^ffcb4aA lonely ghost outside Orchid Temple.\rWith the help of Redglow the Taoist \rand Fang the Scholar she was finally reincarnated.	1	16407	2147483711
41972	AA32FF	Luminoc Architect	^ffcb4aOne of The Seven Wraithbeasts,\rit killed all the people in the Fortress of the \rTalon in order to get the Talon Chart.	1	16407	2147483711
41973	AA32FF	Krixxix	^ffcb4aOne of The Seven Wraithbeasts, \rit led the Adalwolf army to invade the Alliance's camps.	1	16407	2147483711
41974	AA32FF	Gouf, Aerox Chief	^ffcb4aOne of The Seven Wraithbeasts,\rit has two horns and a bat wing,\rand takes Skull Mountain as its base.	1	16407	2147483711
41975	AA32FF	Demonic Feligar	^ffcb4aOne of The Seven Wraithbeasts, \rit led a horde of Wraiths to attack Heaven's Tear.	1	16407	2147483711
41976	AA32FF	Khewy, Rattus Lord	^ffcb4aOne of The Seven Wraithbeasts,\rit tried to open the gateway linking our world together \rwith the other world in order to summon otherworldly \rhorrors to aid them in the war against us.	1	16407	2147483711
41977	AA32FF	Quillhog King	^ffcb4aOne of The Seven Wraithbeasts,\rit led the Wraith legions to invade Tusk Town.	1	16407	2147483711
