41981	8C8CEF	Chief Assassin	^ffcb4aThe Treasure Cave of Nightscream Isle was once one of the \rmost wealthy and luxurious caves around in the world. \rEach night, pirates would haul their booty to this place.\rAmong them, the Chief Assassin is the cruelest.	1	16407	2147483711
41982	8C8CEF	Gang Leader	^ffcb4aThe five races exile their criminals to Tusk Town,\rwhich has become a haven for thieves and brigands.	1	16407	2147483711
41983	8C8CEF	Seaweed Thief	^ffcb4aAfter the Wraiths invaded, Perfect World was \rno longer safe, including Sanctuary. 	1	16407	2147483711
41984	8C8CEF	Seaspray Bladewolf	^ffcb4aSeaspray Bladewolf desired to occupy Dreamweaver Port.\rThanks to General Tuyan's intelligent commands, the port was not destroyed.	1	16407	2147483711
41985	8C8CEF	Araneid Cruelheart	^ffcb4aAraneid Cruelhearts range outside the Camp of the Intrepid.\rThey are fierce and poisonous.	1	16407	2147483711
41986	8C8CEF	Chipmunq Glutton	^ffcb4aChipmunq Gluttons like eating tough stones,\respecially those soaked by Araneid Cruelhearts' venom.	1	16407	2147483711
41987	8C8CEF	Decaying Cleavehand	^ffcb4aNorth of the Camp of the Intrepid live a great number of Decaying Cleavehands.\rThey are tall, ugly and powerful.	1	16407	2147483711
41988	8C8CEF	Nivastok Shieldbearer 	^ffcb4aThe Harshlands are located in the northwestern corner of Perfect World.\rThey is a snow-capped and deserted place, and home to the Nivastok Shieldbearers.\rFerocious but tamable, Nivastok Shieldbearers are one of the best \rcompanions for Venomancers.	1	16407	2147483711
41989	8C8CEF	Malicious Cadevil	^ffcb4aBoth Archosaur and Thousand Streams are encircled by \rthe Wraiths. A huge number of Malicious Cadevils are marching \rtowards East Barrier Village and South Barrier Village.\rThe two villages are covered by the air of death.	1	16407	2147483711
41990	8C8CEF	Headless Knight	^ffcb4aHeadless Knights work for the Wraiths and wreak havoc wherever they go.\rPlease kill them whenever you see them.	1	16407	2147483711
41991	8C8CEF	Acephalic Rider	^ffcb4aRemember, you should overcome the fear in your heart \rin battle with those headless wraiths!	1	16407	2147483711
41992	8C8CEF	Araneid Sharpfang	^ffcb4aThose living in the cold areas of the Midlands once sought the company\rof Snow Hounds, until they were wiped out by the Araneid Sharpfangs.	1	16407	2147483711
41993	8C8CEF	Nivastok Brave	^ffcb4aNivastok Braves carry mysterious amulets that move\rby themselves when placed on the ground, pointing\rthe way to the source of their mystic power.	1	16407	2147483711
41994	8C8CEF	Gnosis Treerat	^ffcb4aGnosis Treerats used to live harmoniously with humans,\rbut the Wraiths corrupted them and turned them into cruel creatures.	1	16407	2147483711
41995	8C8CEF	Dustwraith	^ffcb4aConquesting Dustwraiths live in Sundown Town.\rThey use their cookware as weapons to fight.	1	16407	2147483711
