46910	AA32FF	Anniversary: Kota Pedang	^ffcb4aHere is the place where the dream began and the place\rwhere reality showed its power. Some people started\rtheir heroic dream here, while others surrendered it\rfor a life of peace. However, Etherblade's long history\rproves to the world that those who persevered are worthy\rof respect, and those who returned are to be cherished.	1	16407	2147483711
46911	AA32FF	Anniversary: Kota Siluman	^ffcb4aThe wild Barbarians, the mysterious Venomancers, and the archaic\rbuildings and bestial statues of the Untamed make up the savage\rCity of the Lost. Though these heroes have fought and died in\rbloody battles, none have regretted it. Their true desire, though,\rwas peace, and now that they have achieved it in their home they\rseek to protect the stability and prosperity of the world.	1	16407	2147483711
46912	AA32FF	Anniversary: Kota Samudera	^ffcb4aThe City of Raging Tides lies to the southeast of Perfect World, on Barrier Island\rin the Sea of Reality. Long ago, when the Wraiths first invaded Perfect World, the\rTideborn elders cast a spell called the Dimensional Cataclysm to defeat them, but in\rdoing so their land was cut off from Perfect World for many years. Though they have\rsince returned, so too have their immortal enemies: the vicious Nightspikes.	1	16407	2147483711
46913	AA32FF	Anniversary: Kota Tellus	^ffcb4aTellus City is the home of the Earthguard, warriors chosen by\rRadiance to protect Perfect World from the Wraiths. Though long\rburied beneath the surface, when the Wraiths once again threatened\rPerfect World, they emerged from their long slumber to do battle once more.	1	16407	2147483711
46914	AA32FF	Anniversary: Dawnglory	^ffcb4aThe Reapers were once the children of the Divine Child, but when their\rcreator was struck down they were given mortal lives so as to outlive him.\rTheir descendants, the Nightshades, came to Perfect World aboard a flying ship\rand settled on an uncharted island in the northeast. Expanding their ship into\rthe city of Dawnglory, they have protected Perfect World from within the shadows,\ronly recently stepping into the light to openly battle the Wraiths and Nightmares.	1	16407	2147483711
46915	AA32FF	Anniversary: Kota Peri	^ffcb4aThe Winged Elves are noble and dignified, flying high above Perfect World\ron brilliant feathered wings. Their people are skill Archers and powerful\rClerics, their homes elegant and atmospheric, and their land full of\rforests of idyllic beauty. Beneath the canopy of the great tree lies\rthe beautiful heart of their territory: the City of the Plume.	1	16407	2147483711
