43759	FFD700	Leisure Gift Box	^ffcb4aWith this item you can see the treasure in the Leisure Gift Box. \r^00ffff Right click to use. \rMake sure you have at least one empty slot in your bag.\r^ffcb4aWildheart Jade^FF0000 can get from mainline quests of ^ff00eeAstral Sky^FF0000 in the Primal World\r and daily quest ^ff00eeStrangeness in the Snow^FF0000.	1	16407	0
