50268	8C8CEF	Deco.: Boat Trip Poem II	^FFCB4AImagine floating down the river in a sturdy wooden boat while a woman carefully washes vegetables in the clear water. \r^00FFFFRight-click to use. Can only be used in the Homestead.	99	16403	0
50269	8C8CEF	Deco.: Heart Longing Poem II	^FFCB4AA pure and compassionate heart produces peace and harmony. \r^00FFFFRight-click to use. Can only be used in the Homestead.	99	16403	0
